Patent Information.Patent Title: Anti-tumor active polypeptide and application thereof
Patent Information.Abstract: The invention discloses an anti-tumor active polypeptide and application thereof, wherein the amino acid sequence of the polypeptide is shown as SEQ ID NO. 01. The anti-tumor active polypeptide and the modified variant thereof have strong tumor cell inhibition capability and low killing effect on normal cells.
